# {{projectName}}

## Commands

Install dependencies:

```bash
npm install
```

Start the starter app:

```bash
npm run dev -- --target app
```

Build the starter app:

```bash
npm run build -- --target app
```

Preview the built starter app:

```bash
npm run preview -- --target app
```

Run diagnostics for the starter app:

```bash
npm run diagnose -- --target app
```

Create another app target:

```bash
npm run mainz -- app create my-app
```

Then run it with:

```bash
npm run dev -- --target my-app
```
